   "source": [
    "# Tabla resumen por operador\n",
    "operator_stats = calls.groupby('operator_id').agg({\n",
    "    'calls_count': 'sum',\n",
    "    'is_missed_call': 'mean',\n",
    "    'call_duration': 'mean',\n",
    "    'total_call_duration': 'mean'\n",
    "}).reset_index()\n",
    "\n",
    "# Renombrar columnas para mayor claridad\n",
    "operator_stats.columns = ['operator_id', 'total_calls', 'missed_ratio', 'avg_call_duration', 'avg_total_duration']\n",
    "\n",
    "# Mostrar las primeras filas\n",
    "display(operator_stats.head())"
   ]
  },

       "True     558\n",

       "Name: ineficiente, dtype: int64"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 13,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "# Detectar operadores con bajo rendimiento \n",
    "\n",
    "# Calcular el percentil 25 (umbral bajo)\n",
    "low_call_threshold = operator_stats['total_calls'].quantile(0.25)\n",
    "\n",
    "# Crear columna \"ineficiente\"\n",
    "operator_stats['ineficiente'] = np.where(\n",
    "    (operator_stats['missed_ratio'] > 0.4) | (operator_stats['total_calls'] < low_call_threshold),\n",
    "    True, False\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "# Ver cu谩ntos operadores son ineficaces\n",
    "operator_stats['ineficiente'].value_counts()"
   ]
  },
